videos.description: Nicolas Claxton drives and kicks to Tyree Crump, who absorbs the contact and knocks down the triple for a 4-point play opportunity.
videos.headline: Crump's 4-point play puts Georgia ahead

videos.description: Tyree Crump can't finish in transition, but Nicolas Claxton comes flying in to clean up the miss with a vicious two-handed putback.
videos.headline: Georgia's Claxton throws down nasty putback jam

videos.description: Courtney Ramey turns it over, but gets it right back with a steal, then sends it ahead to Jaxson Hayes for the two-handed fast-break finish.
videos.headline: Hayes slams after helter-skelter sequence

videos.description: Kerwin Roach II finds a lane and takes off for the rim, battling through the contact to throw down a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Roach slams through foul

videos.description: Nicolas Claxton cuts to the rim for a two-handed slam, then pulls up from deep to extend Georgia's lead to 81-71 over Texas.
videos.headline: Claxton extends Bulldogs' lead with dunk, big 3
